text: A Facebook post purportedly shows the text of a letter written by author F. Scott Fitzgerald in 1920 during the Spanish Influenza pandemic.
A letter was written by F. Scott Fitzgerald in 1920 while the author was quarantined in France during the Spanish influenza pandemic.
